data.description: Located in Bentleyville, PA, 24 Hillman St. is a Ranch-style home situated in a QUIET cul-de-sac neighborhood. Discover its VERY SPACIOUS KITCHEN boasting ABUNDANT CABINET SPACE, complemented by THREE WELL-SIZED BEDROOMS, each offering CLOSET SPACE and AMPLE storage. Conveniently located with easy access to I-70 E, this property caters to families seeking convenience and accessibility.
